<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 21:13:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普的备忘录概述了互惠关税计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/trumps-memo-outlining-reciprocal-tariffs-plans-2025-02-13/</link><description>财政部长的备忘录</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 20:47:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/trumps-memo-outlining-reciprocal-tariffs-plans-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>独家：特朗普准备改变美国芯片法案条件，消息人士称</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-prepares-change-us-chips-act-conditions-sources-say-2025-02-13/</link><description>熟悉此事的两个消息人士告诉路透社，白宫正在寻求重新谈判美国筹码和科学法案奖，并表示延误了一些即将到来的半导体支出。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 20:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-prepares-change-us-chips-act-conditions-sources-say-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普警告金砖国家可能面临100％的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-warns-brics-nations-could-face-100-tariffs-2025-02-13/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周四表示，金砖国家可能“如果想和美元玩游戏”，可能会面临100％的关税。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 19:42:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-warns-brics-nations-could-face-100-tariffs-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普说，蒂克托克的截止日期可能会延长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-says-tiktok-deadline-could-be-extended-2025-02-13/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周四表示，他在执行对受欢迎的短视频应用程序Tiktok禁令的75天延误可能会扩大，但他说他认为这是不必要的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 19:21:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-says-tiktok-deadline-could-be-extended-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>蒙克勒（Moncler）的2024年结果超过了中国的帮助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/moncler-posts-2024-results-above-expectations-helped-by-china-2025-02-13/</link><description>意大利外套制造商蒙克勒（Moncler）的收入在第四季度以恒定的汇率增长了8％，高于分析师的预期，在中国大陆的双位数字增长方面，该品牌的同名品牌和销售提高了其Stone Island Label。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 17:01:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/moncler-posts-2024-results-above-expectations-helped-by-china-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交大臣十年来首次在英国举行会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-china-talks-cover-contentious-issues-2025-02-13/</link><description>中国外交大臣王伊（Wang Yi）于十年来首次与总理，外交大臣和国家安全顾问进行会谈，这是他第一次对英国进行了正式访问。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 11:12:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-china-talks-cover-contentious-issues-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>部长说，英国上市是“黄金标准”。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-should-regulate-companies-doing-business-country-minister-says-when-asked-2025-02-13/</link><description>英国商务大臣说，当询问中国在线零售商Shein浮动的意图时，伦敦上市就环境，劳动和税收法规方面设定了“黄金标准”，以应对任何道德危险的风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 11:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-should-regulate-companies-doing-business-country-minister-says-when-asked-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国看到“深入”的库克群岛会谈，预计合作伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-sees-in-depth-cook-islands-talks-partnership-deal-expected-2025-02-13/</link><description>中国在周四首次承认库克群岛领导人的访问是在新西兰愤怒的情况下，没有咨询过涉及南太平洋国家的预期协议，惠灵顿与惠灵顿建立了宪法联系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:50:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-sees-in-depth-cook-islands-talks-partnership-deal-expected-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>黄金的照明跑步在印度的婚礼季节，中国提供折扣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/golds-lighting-run-rains-indias-wedding-season-china-offers-discounts-2025-02-13/</link><description>一场杰出的集会将全球黄金价格提高到历史最高高价，在印度的婚礼季节购买了珠宝的阴影，而中国的经销商为吸引买家提供了折扣。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 10:25:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/golds-lighting-run-rains-indias-wedding-season-china-offers-discounts-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>越南使用中国贷款，以83亿美元的铁路连接两国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-use-chinese-loans-83-billion-railway-linking-both-countries-2025-02-13/</link><description>运输部长周四表示，越南计划从中国政府那里获得贷款，部分资助了一个83亿美元的项目，以建造一条新的铁路，将两国联系起来。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 07:46:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-use-chinese-loans-83-billion-railway-linking-both-countries-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴将与Apple合作，获得AI功能，将股票送至3年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/alibaba-chairman-confirms-ai-partnership-with-apple-chinese-iphones-2025-02-13/</link><description>其主席周四表示，阿里巴巴将与苹果公司合作，以支持iPhone的AI服务产品。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 06:51:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/alibaba-chairman-confirms-ai-partnership-with-apple-chinese-iphones-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚和中国对南中国海战斗机事件的责任责备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-criticises-unsafe-chinese-fighter-jet-interaction-south-china-sea-2025-02-13/</link><description>澳大利亚对中国周四所说的话引起了人们的关注，这是两天前中国战斗机对南中国海的澳大利亚海事巡逻队的“不安全和不专业”的行动，这是北京争议的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 06:21:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-criticises-unsafe-chinese-fighter-jet-interaction-south-china-sea-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>法国的勒格兰德（Legrand</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/frances-legrand-see-30-million-impact-us-tariffs-chinese-goods-2025-02-13/</link><description>首席执行官BenoîtCoquart告诉路透社，法国电气和数字基础设施集团勒格兰德（Legrand）并未将美国关税视为一个战略问题，并期望美国10％的美国关税对中国进口的财务影响约为3000万美元。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 06:16:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/frances-legrand-see-30-million-impact-us-tariffs-chinese-goods-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国的腾讯在美国地方法院赢得视频侵犯案件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinas-tencent-wins-video-copyright-infringment-case-us-district-court-2025-02-13/</link><description>在发现总部位于台湾的电视盒公司Unblock Tech和其他发行商侵犯了这家中国科技巨头开发的视频内容的版权之后，美国地方法院已授予了近8500万美元的赔偿金。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 05:56:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinas-tencent-wins-video-copyright-infringment-case-us-district-court-2025-02-13/</guid></item><item><title>WSJ报道说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-pushes-peacekeeping-efforts-end-ukraine-war-wsj-reports-2025-02-13/</link><description>《华尔街日报》报道说，中国已经提出了一项提议，要求在俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京和美国总统唐纳德·特朗普之间举行峰会，以帮助结束乌克兰战争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 04:16:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-pushes-peacekeeping-efforts-end-ukraine-war-wsj-reports-2025-02-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>